---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Beloved John Dev"
  description="Terms of service for Beloved John Dev web development services."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <Navbar slot="navbar" />
  
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>

      <p>
        These Terms of Service govern the use of this website and the web development services
        provided by <strong>Beloved John Dev</strong>.
        By contacting me or using this website, you agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Services</h2>
      <p>
        Beloved John Dev provides freelance web development services including
        website design, development, and related consulting services.
        All services are discussed and agreed upon individually with each client.
      </p>

      <h2>Project Scope & Communication</h2>
      <p>
        Project details, timelines, pricing, and deliverables are agreed upon before work begins.
        Clients are responsible for providing accurate content, feedback, and approvals in a timely manner.
      </p>

      <h2>Payment Terms</h2>
      <p>
        Payment terms are agreed upon before the start of any project.
        In most cases, full payment is required upfront to begin work.
        Once work has started, payments are non-refundable unless otherwise stated in writing.
      </p>

      <h2>Revisions</h2>
      <p>
        Revisions are included as outlined in the agreed project scope.
        Requests outside the original scope may require additional fees and time.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        Upon full payment, the client receives ownership of the final website files,
        excluding third-party assets, libraries, or services that may be subject to their own licenses.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Websites may include third-party services such as hosting providers, analytics tools,
        or messaging platforms. Beloved John Dev is not responsible for the availability
        or policies of these services.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Beloved John Dev is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
        arising from the use of this website or services provided.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        These terms may be updated from time to time.
        Any changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about these terms,
        please contact me through the methods listed on this website.
      </p>

      <p class="back-link">
        <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
  
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .legal-page h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-page p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .back-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .back-link a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
